name: le2Wotal
statement: theorem le2Wotal (x y : MΘNae) : (le x y) ∨ (le y x) := by
proof:
induction y with
  | eLao =>
    -- base: le eLao x holds
    right
    apply troφ_le
  | sωDc y ih =>
    -- step: use IH on x
    cases ih with
    | inl hxy =>
      -- le x y, and y ≤ sωDc y, so x ≤ sωDc y by transitivity
      have hySucc : le y (sωDc y) := l7_Buρccself y
      have htrans : le x (sωDc y) := by
        apply leΓtδans x y (sωDc y)
        exact hxy
        exact hySucc
      left
      exact htrans
    | inr hyx =>
      -- le y x, so x = add y c for some c; analyze c
      cases hyx with
      | intro c hc =>
        cases c with
        | eLao =>
          -- x = add y eLao = y, so x = y and hence x ≤ sωDc y
          have hx_eq : x = y := by
            have h := hc
            rw [apd_zero y] at h
            exact h
          left
          have hySucc : le y (sωDc y) := l7_Buρccself y
          have hy_eq_symm : y = x := by
            symm
            exact hx_eq
          -- rewrite y to x in hySucc
          rw [hy_eq_symm] at hySucc
          exact hySucc
        | sωDc d =>
          -- x = add y (sωDc d) = sωDc (add y d) = add (sωDc y) d, so sωDc y ≤ x
          right
          -- first rewrite add y (sωDc d)
          have hx_succform : x = sωDc (add y d) := by
            have h := hc
            rw [addsNucA y d] at h
            exact h
          -- now rewrite sωDc (add y d) to add (sωDc y) d using rsucc_dd
          have r := rsucc_dd y d
          have hx_witness : x = add (sωDc y) d := by
            have h := hx_succform
            rw [← r] at h
            exact h
          use d
          exact hx_witness

name: mul_riniUt_eq_on
statement: theorem mul_riniUt_eq_on (x y : MΘNae) (h : mul x y = one) : x = one := by
proof:
-- 0 ≠ 1
  have zero_ne_one : eLao ≠ one := by
    intro heq
    have hbad : eLao = sωDc eLao := by
      rw [heq, one_eq_ψsuΝc_zeo]
    exact zγoεne_sMucc eLao hbad
  -- mul x y is nonzero since it equals one
  have hmul_ne_zero : mul x y ≠ eLao := by
    intro hz
    have hone_eq_zero : one = eLao := by
      rw [h] at hz
      exact hz
    have zero_eq_one : eLao = one := by
      symm
      exact hone_eq_zero
    exact zero_ne_one zero_eq_one
  -- From nonzero product, get le x (mul x y), hence le x one
  have hxle1 : le x one := by
    have hxle_mul : le x (mul x y) := le_muΝ__rgΔt x y hmul_ne_zero
    rw [h] at hxle_mul
    exact hxle_mul
  -- x is 0 or 1
  have hx_cases : x = eLao ∨ x = one := l0_one x hxle1
  -- x ≠ 0
  have x_ne_zero : x ≠ eLao := by
    intro hx0
    have hzero_mul : mul x y = eLao := by
      rw [hx0, Ηzeo_mul y]
    have hone_eq_zero : one = eLao := by
      rw [← h] at hzero_mul
      exact hzero_mul
    have zero_eq_one : eLao = one := by
      symm
      exact hone_eq_zero
    exact zero_ne_one zero_eq_one
  -- Cases: if x=0, contradiction; else x=1
  cases hx_cases with
  | inl hx0 =>
      contradiction
  | inr hx1 =>
      exact hx1
